 can city dwellers help with climate change? Buy less stuff.\n |date=11 June 2019\n |website=National Geographic\n}}\n** {{Cite web  |ref={{harvid|National Geographic, 13 August|2019}}\n |last = Welch   |first = Craig\n |url=https://www.nationalgeographic.com/environment/2019/08/arctic-permafrost-is-thawing-it-could-speed-up-climate-change-feature/\n |title=Arctic permafrost is thawing fast. That affects us all.\n |date=13 August 2019\n |website=National Geographic\n |access-date=25 August 2019}}\n*''[[National Review]]''\n** {{Cite news   |ref={{harvid|National Review, 27 February|2014}}\n |url=https://www.nationalreview.com/corner/climate-change-will-cause-rape-and-murder-and-assault-and-robbery-and-larceny-and-make/\n |title=Climate Change Will Cause Rape and Murder and Assault and Robbery and Larceny and Make People Steal Your Car\n |date=27 February 2014\n |work=National Review\n |access-date=17 November 2018}}\n*''[[National Science Digital Library]]''\n** {{cite web |first=James R. |last=Fleming | title= Climate Change and Anthropogenic Greenhouse Warming: A Selection of Key Articles, 1824\u20131995, with Interpretive Essays | website=National Science Digital Library Project Archive PALE:ClassicArticles | date=17 March 2008 | url=http://nsdl.library.cornell.edu/websites/wiki/index.php/PALE_ClassicArticles/GlobalWarming.html | ref=harv | access-date=7 October 2019}}\n*''[[Nature (journal)|Nature]]''\n** {{cite news |ref=harv\n |last= Schiermeier    |first= Quirin\n |date= 7 July 2015   \n |title = Climate scientists discuss future of their field\n |doi= 10.1038/nature.2015.17917\n |publisher = Nature\n |url = https://www.nature.com/news/climate-scientists-discuss-future-of-their-field-1.17917\n |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011182255/http://www.nature.com/news/climate-scientists-discuss-future-of-their-field-1.17917\n |archive-date=11 October 2017|url-status=live\n}}\n**{{cite journal    |ref=harv\n |last =Crucifix  |first =Michel\n |date =2016